is take advantage of us.

16:11.541 --> 16:13.666
According
to my junior pocket encyclopedia,

16:13.750 --> 16:14.625
you're a dick.

16:14.708 --> 16:17.375
Fine, I was leaving anyway.

16:17.458 --> 16:20.916
Put me back in your bike basket
and bring me back where you found me.

16:22.125 --> 16:24.458
-Well?
-You can walk to the bikes.

16:25.750 --> 16:28.666
Oh, your Earth atmosphere,
it's like poison.

16:28.750 --> 16:30.083
Carry me!

16:31.833 --> 16:33.208
Yeah, that's right.

16:33.291 --> 16:35.000
Carry me, you swine.

16:42.416 --> 16:44.333
Okay, Brett, it's no big deal.

16:44.416 --> 16:46.875
You just wanna stay here
a little longer with your friends.

16:46.958 --> 16:49.041
Just a couple spritzes of Nostalgia Max,

16:49.708 --> 16:52.875
and they will love it here
as much as you do.

16:52.958 --> 16:53.958
Oh no. No, no.

16:54.041 --> 16:55.291
Fuck!

16:58.750 --> 17:01.708
